text: Xenuroturris is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Turridae, the turrids. ==Species== Species within the genus Xenuroturris include: * † Xenuroturris antiselli (F. Anderson & B. Martin, 1914) * Xenuroturris castanella Powell, 1964 * Xenuroturris cerithiformis Powell, 1964: synonym of Iotyrris cerithiformis (Powell, 1964) * Xenuroturris cingulifera (Lamarck, 1822): synonym of Iotyrris cingulifera (Lamarck, 1822) * Xenuroturris emmae Bozzetti, 1993 * Xenuroturris gemmuloides Powell, 1967 * Xenuroturris kingae Powell, 1964 * Xenuroturris legitima Iredale, 1929 * Xenuroturris millepunctata (Sowerby III, 1908) ==References== ==External links== * Category:Turridae
title: Xenuroturris
